{"tid":1775270,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行動一定無問題，不被捕，不被咬先係重點。","createTime":"2019-12-08T17:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T18:34:17.000Z","uid":289040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f546190b832b7a65472dd08bf07eb0c53baf139","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:52:55.000Z","msg":"只要做到不被捕，我話知你流血定受傷，都可以再出過黎。黎明行動精要既地方唔係玩一日咁簡單。就算唔係每日行動都要做到間唔中行動一日。<br />\n返工撚真係好中意返工，你阻佢三五日佢會覺得你麻撚煩，阻住揾食，但你阻佢三五個月，佢就會習慣左你班人存在，會轉目標呀明唔明。<br />\n和理非方面完全係唔會再好似以前咁割蓆。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武勇武勇武一定一定一定要不被捕不被捕不被捕</span></strong>，行動失敗絕對唔係問題，最多下次再黎過。<br />\n和勇不分就是香港人既團結。"},{"pid":"c8f25ca6916ba329776b2bf6ed7ba4217a3ba6b5","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"p牌無得推"},{"pid":"eac6950221b57daa008b403989c286fb9d91f137","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"不被捕"},{"pid":"bf4815a064fc819a4e968939fbae44ff6323957b","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:56:59.000Z","msg":"不被咬"},{"pid":"a3925a030b9f0b2e869b83874fcdb82e6b3043c6","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:59:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"51566e16799d24e2cd412a068e82d02081fabc84","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T17:59:25.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"dc85bf6b31834bcef3401a172491b31c253b7198","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:00:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"5365fb30caaaf4dbd17ad7db589a296932283f15","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T18:00:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c7397aa8088cbb0c4541bd9b165979d856b99893","tid":1775270,"uid":289040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08